               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="186010220136"></xptr>
               <p>these trousers (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>) are mine—I saw them safe at my door, and missed them two minutes afterwards—I saw the prisoner running away with them on his arm, and the lad running after him—I overtook him, brought him back, and gave him in custody—he said that they were not mine, and he should not give them to me—they have my mark on them—he was quite sober—I had been watching him three-quarters of an hour.</p>
               <p>
