                  </hi>. I am in the service of the last witness—I was mind<lb></lb>ing his shop on this Saturday night—the prisoner came up and said, "That is a nice pair of trousers"—I said, "Yes"—he said, "They are mine"—I said "If you do not put them down I shall call Mr. Turner"—he said "Well, I am off"—I called Mr. Turner, who ran after him.</p>
